        "title": "Thread to handle Large List of objects in Java",
        "body": "<p>I have a very large <code>ArrayList<\/code> of object, it executes smoothly in a single thread. but execution time is the factor. <\/p>\n\n<p>Let my list has 50 elements, and I have 3 threads,<\/p>\n\n<p>I would like 1st thread will process 0 to 15 and 2nd thread will process 16 to 31 and rest of the process will process by the third thread.<\/p>\n\n<p>Is it possible?<\/p>\n",
